TextEng: I will help you, if I can.
I have no time for this.
I want to ask you some questions.
I might help you... if the price is right.
Me help, if me can.
Me not got time for this!
Me want ask stuff.
Me help if you give gold.
Goodbye.
What kind of heirloom? Let me see.
Okay, I'll help you.
What you mean, heirloom? You show me reward.
Text: 가보 무슨 말이야? 너 보상 보여줘.

TextEng: Okay, me help you.
Forget it. Show me the heirloom or no Leesa.
Text: 됐어. 가보를 보여주든지 아니면 리사는 없어.

TextEng: You no show me reward, me no get your sister.
Text: 너 보상 안 보여주면, 나 네 여동생 안 찾아.

TextEng: Didn't you look for her?
Where did you last see her?
Don't worry, I'll bring her back!
Why you not look for your sister?
Where you last see sister?
You not be sad. Me bring sister back!
Your sister is dead.
Sister be dead.
No, but I am still looking.
No, but me still look.
Text: 아니, 근데 나 아직 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Forget it. I've changed my mind.
Me not help no more. Me change me mind.
Text: 나 이제 안 도와. 나 마음 바뀌었어.

TextEng: Thank you.
Keep your cloak. You need it more than I do.
Text: 망토는 가져. 나보다 네가 더 필요해.

TextEng: You keep cloak. Me got lots stuff. You need cloak more. You look cold.
Text: 너 망토 가져. 나 물건 많아. 너 망토 더 필요해. 너 추워 보여.
